# Accessibility Test Cases (WCAG Awareness)

## Scope
Ensures basic accessibility compliance and usability for all users.

---

## TC_ACC_001 – Keyboard Navigation Support
Expected: Full navigation possible without mouse.

## TC_ACC_002 – Screen Reader Compatibility
Expected: Logical reading order and alt text.

## TC_ACC_003 – Contrast Ratio
Expected: Text readable in normal and high contrast mode.

## TC_ACC_004 – Form Error Announcements
Expected: Errors are announced clearly to assistive tools.

## TC_ACC_005 – Focus Visible
Expected: Focus highlight visible clearly.
